  "markup": "Join Douglas Johnson, ATC as he presents a webinar focused on understanding the clinical application of super pulsed laser and light treatment (SPLT) and how to get the best outcomes.\u0026nbsp; This introductory course will focus on:\u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nThe Clinician\u0026rsquo;s Take On: HOW IT WORKS\u003Cbr /\u003E\nDose, Dose, Dose: Stimulation vs Inhibition\u003Cbr /\u003E\nKnowing Your Equipment: LaserStim and LaserShower\u003Cbr /\u003E\nQuick Start: Getting Success from Day 1 using basic protocols"
}]]></Value>
